<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample response: I disagree with Tyler. The side does look longer than 4 meters, but I think it is 6 meters long. If we add the missing side to the 6 meter side, they need to add to 12 meters to match the other side of the figure. This is because in a rectangle, the sides opposite each other have to be the same length.</p>
  </solution>


